##  Dataset Information

* Dataset Type: Employee / HR data
* Data Includes:

  * Employee ID
  * Employee Name
  * Department
  * Gender
  * Age
  * Salary
  * Designation
  * Joining Date (if available)

---

##  Key KPIs (Measures)

* Total Employees
* Average Salary
* Department-wise Employee Count
* Gender Ratio
* Highest & Lowest Salary

---

##  Visualizations Used

* KPI Cards â€“ total employees, average salary
* Bar Chart â€“ department-wise employee count
* Pie / Donut Chart â€“ gender distribution
* Column Chart â€“ salary comparison
* Table â€“ employee details

---

##  Insights from the Report

* Identified departments with highest employee strength
* Analyzed salary distribution across departments
* Observed gender balance in the organization
* Compared average salaries by department/designation

